      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ethical review of the human-subjects research is transferred to QMUL's Devolved School Research Ethics Committee (DSREC, ref DSEECS25.094); the\nevaluation protocol was reviewed and approved before any participant data was collected, and the committee's conditions on consent, anonymity, and\nwithdrawal are followed",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "edBkZSbF3YmzXjtedveel",
      "originalText": "Ethical review of the human-subjects research is transferred to QMUL's Devolved School Research Ethics Committee (DSREC, ref DSEECS25.094); the evaluation protocol was reviewed and approved before any participant data was collected, and the committee's conditions on consent, anonymity, and withdrawal are followed",
