      "text": "Agents can only emit predefined actions and only call data tools through a fixed allowlist, so even if the underlying language model misbehaves it cannot\nperform actions outside the closed set",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wfVw09EKa384I0DdBCAFp",
      "originalText": "Agents can only emit predefined actions and only call data tools through a fixed allowlist, so even if the underlying language model misbehaves it cannot perform actions outside the closed set",
