      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971690194,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"One LLM call,\none structured\nresponse.\"",
      "fontSize": 102.25112661176303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"One LLM call, one structured response.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-tuPflD0_yJV7m0jY2Dm3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3463.3111738733623,
      "y": 4148.778831549924,
      "width": 1592.3453786770053,
      "height": 486.4215915936009,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 457140588,
      "version": 398,
      "versionNonce": 1051806700,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972350394,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "As a student submitting a news article, I\nwant my article to pass through a single\nstep rather than multiple LLM calls, so\nthat token spend stays predictable and I\ncan get to the learning part quickly",
      "fontSize": 77.82745465497615,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "As a student submitting a news article, I want my article to pass through a single step rather than multiple LLM calls, so that token spend stays predictable and I can get to the learning part quickly",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aXWW0zSWw5y6jagpeceNn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1451.967093695995,
      "y": 3501.8700540744926,
      "width": 2026.0429434420123,
      "height": 309.63117101294426,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2074210900,
      "version": 178,
      "versionNonce": 595160812,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971719710,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "One-shot Gate Agent validation,\nsummary, and company extraction",
      "fontSize": 123.8524684051777,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "One-shot Gate Agent validation, summary, and company extraction",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "M0hXHuk7aMHvaMUxdjaOa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1494.8821804673341,
      "y": 4088.4479816068497,
      "width": 2071.9626918267104,
      "height": 1115.437236709812,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5S",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 32104660,
      "version": 140,
      "versionNonce": 541561324,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971804643,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once an article passes the basic length and\nduplicate gates, the system hands it to the\nGate Agent. The Gate Agent makes exactly\none LLM call at temperature 0 and asks for a\nstructured JSON response containing three\nthings: whether the article is valid business\nnews, a short summary, and the list of\ncompanies mentioned. If the response is\nmalformed, the Gate Agent retries up to three\ntimes.",
      "fontSize": 89.23497893678496,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once an article passes the basic length and duplicate gates, the system hands it to the Gate Agent. The Gate Agent makes exactly one LLM call at temperature 0 and asks for a structured JSON response containing three things: whether the article is valid business news, a short summary, and the list of companies mentioned. If the response is malformed, the Gate Agent retries up to three times.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zmFer9ve4541Zi_J8KYNP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1490.5708425006455,
      "y": 5531.010789441602,
      "width": 2072.8089506050846,
      "height": 478.7560612424065,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 649403500,
      "version": 237,
      "versionNonce": 1058698604,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971803127,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Doing validation, summary, and extraction in\none call keeps token spend predictable.\nTemperature 0 makes the result\nreproducible, which matters for tests.",
      "fontSize": 95.7512122484813,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Doing validation, summary, and extraction in one call keeps token spend predictable. Temperature 0 makes the result reproducible, which matters for tests.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Szrn7frZ1c46kVAmSkiXL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1487.7132594421228,
      "y": 6380.721567953307,
      "width": 1880.5870739479506,
      "height": 248.54148371577708,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5U",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1924872148,
      "version": 136,
      "versionNonce": 1268350956,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971828661,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A student submits an article that is\nlong enough and is not a duplicate.",
      "fontSize": 99.41659348631083,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A student submits an article that is long enough and is not a duplicate.",
