    },
    {
      "id": "7tZIyzib1MyBTN6OVDsJ_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 966.6259429283826,
      "y": 3570.5959522838,
      "width": 1498.1265920223545,
      "height": 1055.2556221602863,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 382839892,
      "version": 186,
      "versionNonce": 1808610412,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972294406,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1- The submitted article is\nat least 50 characters long\n2- The article is not a\nduplicate of one already in\nthe database\n3- The OpenAI API is\nreachable\n",
      "fontSize": 105.52556221602863,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1- The submitted article is at least 50 characters long\n2- The article is not a duplicate of one already in the database\n3- The OpenAI API is reachable\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p4okF-qTahp0LLBfK3UVq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2931.4959364376036,
      "y": 3603.5045850202364,
      "width": 1498.1265920223545,
      "height": 1187.162574930322,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5YV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1172203884,
      "version": 241,
      "versionNonce": 152988372,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972118951,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1- The pipeline hands the\narticle to the Gate Agent\n2- The Gate Agent issues\nexactly one LLM call at\ntemperature 0\n3- The LLM returns a JSON\nresponse, possibly wrapped in\nmarkdown code fences\n",
      "fontSize": 105.52556221602863,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1- The pipeline hands the article to the Gate Agent\n2- The Gate Agent issues exactly one LLM call at temperature 0\n3- The LLM returns a JSON response, possibly wrapped in markdown code fences\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VYKk4Bci1uPx4TVb2B3Ym",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 940.8086774555113,
      "y": 5400.377938462258,
      "width": 1498.1265920223545,
      "height": 1582.8834332404294,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Yl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1793760876,
      "version": 367,
      "versionNonce": 1640557396,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972124080,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1- The Gate Agent parses\nthe JSON and returns\n{isValid, companies[],\nsummary}\n2- Markdown code fences\nare stripped before parsing\n3- The call is configured at\ntemperature 0 so identical\ninputs produce identical\noutputs\n\n",
      "fontSize": 105.52556221602863,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1- The Gate Agent parses the JSON and returns {isValid, companies[], summary}\n2- Markdown code fences are stripped before parsing\n3- The call is configured at temperature 0 so identical inputs produce identical outputs\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "X0Cqst3vBuwAxi-YwIJJk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3398.6667594924866,
      "y": 5633.28642408465,
      "width": 1591.5577682357775,
      "height": 791.4417166202147,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Yp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1565784788,
      "version": 553,
      "versionNonce": 29330668,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972360442,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1- Agent identity generation\nhappens after this step\n2- Duplicate detection runs\nbefore this step\n\n",
      "fontSize": 105.52556221602863,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1- Agent identity generation happens after this step\n2- Duplicate detection runs before this step\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4sGWFA44XtZVremS07GLe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2938.319588621831,
      "y": 5336.517735682429,
      "width": 1558.557667024034,
      "height": 1846.697338780501,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Yt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 861668180,
      "version": 446,
      "versionNonce": 1152478676,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778972297314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1- If the LLM returns\nmalformed JSON, the Gate\nAgent retries up to 3 times\n2- If all three retries fail,\nthe Gate Agent throws an\nerror and the submission is\nrejected\n3- If isValid is false, the\narticle is rejected with the\nLLM's rejectionReason\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 105.52556221602863,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1- If the LLM returns malformed JSON, the Gate Agent retries up to 3 times\n2- If all three retries fail, the Gate Agent throws an error and the submission is rejected\n3- If isValid is false, the article is rejected with the LLM's rejectionReason\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FQyPN0-U1rqTOjiYezQU1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1298.4302519887415,
      "y": 4777.117276402772,
      "width": 599.2399291992188,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 226896620,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1469145068,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778971864005,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
